				<td colspan="2"><span>Hi I am relatively new as a bard. 
<br />

<br />
I have played EQ for 4 years and this is my second attempt as a Bard and it is going much smoother this time. 
<br />

<br />
I am level 34 and I am kiting level 39 and 40 stonegrabbers with very little problems although it does take upwards of 10 mins to kill them but very nice experience. I am using level 30 song Fulfils Curtailing Chant and using my Thunderous Drum of Karana I am doing 33 dmg a tick. 
<br />

<br />
Now I have tried swarming the 3 mushrooms at the entrance to DSP they are all DB to me using Level 18 song Denons Disruptive Discord and my brass instrument Mcxavious Horn of war and it does 27 dmg per tick to all in range. Problem with the swarming is I keep going out of range and when I close in I get swarmed any tips? 
<br />

<br />
Obviously swarming would generate more experience quicker but not if I keep dieing, ootherwise its back to kiting and shouder ache. 
<br />

<br />
Regards 
<br />

<br />
Jizar</span></td>
