				<td colspan="2"><span>To get the most experience from swarm kiting, you kill your ex-pet by DoTs before getting another pet.  Once the ex-pet is dead then you charm another pet to sic to the swarm.  Try to get your pet get beat up as low as you can before breaking charm so that you don't have to DoT em as long.  This will all depend on what you use for invis and also how hard the mobs hit and how big the swarm.
<br />

<br />
As for having a pet while killing the ex-pet, I think you can loose up to 1/3 max the exp if the pet is doing all the damage.</span></td>
